{"tid":2295422,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"究竟喺香港養寵物對佢地黎講係咪好事？","createTime":"2020-11-21T19:14:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-28T07:53:16.000Z","uid":193084,"like":6,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"4c3753c2a1c25b20a67d712d11997c0ea4d880ac","tid":2295422,"uid":193084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T19:14:11.000Z","msg":"點解養寵物？一句講哂咪就係貪佢地得意。真係大愛嘅又有幾多個？正如你喺連登周不時見到有人領養流浪貓，但有幾可見到有人領養流浪狗？因為流浪狗唔得意<br />\n<br />\n可能有人話自己係貓奴，好愛自己隻貓，但困佢喺個幾百呎單位（有人直頭籠養）成世真係一件好事？我以前喺外國生活過一段時間，佢地d貓貓狗狗基本上係放養，平時周圍走，定時定候就識得返屋企食飯，咁先係正常應有嘅生活。<br />\n<br />\n不過都興幸而家香港放狗嘅配套多咗，早十幾年見過d親戚朋友隻狗成世真係得睇醫生果時先會出街（喺個狗袋入面），依d狗個樣通常都好無神氣又神經質咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後我都想問吓貓狗繁殖除咗賺錢仲有咩好處？領養代替購買係咪就好偉大？我有時反而覺得d流浪貓狗喺外面天生天養都好過比人執返屋企失去自由...<br />\n<br />\n希望有人認真討論吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fdf23be8e37ecbe0d69daab54df06988a7dfb4c","tid":2295422,"uid":227788,"like":4,"dislike":10,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T19:36:44.000Z","msg":"大部分都係為咗滿足自己嘅私慾<br />\n<br />\n全部狗公都冇曬啲睾丸 變曬公公<br />\n就係為咗唔好強姦自己隻腳<br />\n<br />\n主人虛偽咁話為咗佢好少啲病痛..."},{"pid":"8e9224c0955d0ee588a0c02f63b05b51d7d7b8cf","tid":2295422,"uid":217332,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T19:41:38.000Z","msg":"我定時會放下啲貓，佢哋又通屋跑，成日都同佢地玩捉依因。食嘢又會就住佢個份量。<br />\n唔覺得自己有虧待咗佢哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc3dc5fb07631a7bee0baffb1316eef1fa8ef832","tid":2295422,"uid":186600,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"8e9224c0955d0ee588a0c02f63b05b51d7d7b8cf","tid":2295422,"uid":217332,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T19:41:38.000Z","msg":"我定時會放下啲貓，佢哋又通屋跑，成日都同佢地玩捉依因。食嘢又會就住佢個份量。<br />\n唔覺得自己有虧待咗佢哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T19:44:02.000Z","msg":"無錯，只要真心覺得佢地開心，無什<br />\n麼不好"},{"pid":"95a5dccc66d5f1422eb4ce27aeadecd91f016f30","tid":2295422,"uid":217332,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8e9224c0955d0ee588a0c02f63b05b51d7d7b8cf","tid":2295422,"uid":217332,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T19:41:38.000Z","msg":"我定時會放下啲貓，佢哋又通屋跑，成日都同佢地玩捉依因。食嘢又會就住佢個份量。<br />\n唔覺得自己有虧待咗佢哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T19:44:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a562a5adf2c2fec86003084dc96a29a938d14ed8","tid":2295422,"uid":32577,"like":8,"dislike":3,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T01:30:11.000Z","msg":"岩呀，應該有得佢地流浪，生滿蝨，成個肚都係蟲，日灑雨淋，日日提心吊膽怕俾車撞，俾變態佬虐殺，捱餓"},{"pid":"1c3c66344ce4ef7c4201896011bda00de87b4dde","tid":2295422,"uid":375352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T01:32:29.000Z","msg":"我有兩隻領養貓<br />\n開大門佢地都唔出去"},{"pid":"3bd6b0184bac1c7cd50a8d9dfc63c94a54daa48d","tid":2295422,"uid":44046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T01:56:18.000Z","msg":"家貓殺雀能力驚人<br />\n我唔會放養<br />\n但會綁貓帶出街<br />\n<br />\n利申 冇養<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.natgeomedia.com/environment/article/content-12117.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.natgeomedia.com%2Fenvironment%2Farticle%2Fcontent-12117.html&d=yoW5vjLKqvFTs4XLOvP5r6zbj60slk4H2lWqI%2F1XlBQ%3D&h=79886af7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.natgeomedia.com/environment/article/content-12117.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/nature/%E6%BE%B3%E6%B4%B2%E8%B2%93%E6%97%A5%E6%AE%BA%E7%99%BE%E8%90%AC%E5%8E%9F%E7%94%9F%E9%9B%80%E9%B3%A5/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fnature%2F%25E6%25BE%25B3%25E6%25B4%25B2%25E8%25B2%2593%25E6%2597%25A5%25E6%25AE%25BA%25E7%2599%25BE%25E8%2590%25AC%25E5%258E%259F%25E7%2594%259F%25E9%259B%2580%25E9%25B3%25A5%2F&d=yoW5vjLKqvFTs4XLOvP5r6zbj60slk4H2lWqI%2F1XlBQ%3D&h=0234fa5f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fnature%2F%25E6%25BE%25B3%25E6%25B4%25B2%25E8%25B2%2593%25E6%2597%25A5%25E6%25AE%25BA%25E7%2599%25BE%25E8%2590%25AC%25E5%258E%259F%25E7%2594%259F%25E9%259B%2580%25E9%25B3%25A5%2F&h=20de159c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/nature/%E6%BE%B3%E6%B4%B2%E8%B2%93%E6%97%A5%E6%AE%BA%E7%99%BE%E8%90%AC%E5%8E%9F%E7%94%9F%E9%9B%80%E9%B3%A5/</a>"},{"pid":"94790a856120d7fd63e55416fc7b966996a54051","tid":2295422,"uid":185238,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"8e9224c0955d0ee588a0c02f63b05b51d7d7b8cf","tid":2295422,"uid":217332,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T19:41:38.000Z","msg":"我定時會放下啲貓，佢哋又通屋跑，成日都同佢地玩捉依因。食嘢又會就住佢個份量。<br />\n唔覺得自己有虧待咗佢哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T03:54:56.000Z","msg":"因為你用人類生活模式作為前題"},{"pid":"72d6c873f0c7afde9d55fabaebd5adf13538409c","tid":2295422,"uid":384783,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T04:36:45.000Z","msg":"其實點先係對寵物好？個好嘅標準係咩野？<br />\n<br />\n我個人覺得係食好住好之外俾佢自己選擇嘅自由。<br />\n<br />\nbtw其實呢啲都係按人類嘅喜好定，所以我覺得都係自己養得開心就算。"},{"pid":"c9e12a1f879a4b293cd60c51e0e0c8266beccfc9","tid":2295422,"uid":193084,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2fdf23be8e37ecbe0d69daab54df06988a7dfb4c","tid":2295422,"uid":227788,"like":4,"dislike":10,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T19:36:44.000Z","msg":"大部分都係為咗滿足自己嘅私慾<br />\n<br />\n全部狗公都冇曬啲睾丸 變曬公公<br />\n就係為咗唔好強姦自己隻腳<br />\n<br />\n主人虛偽咁話為咗佢好少啲病痛..."},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T05:04:31.000Z","msg":"依個問題我都諗咗好耐，我諗主要都係想佢地長命d陪你耐d<br />\n<br />\n但我喺你十幾廿歲精力旺盛果時閹咗你，話你會長命十幾廿年你肯唔肯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74682128d2b5e4c6971b2448e27bb2e7e2967914","tid":2295422,"uid":193084,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"8e9224c0955d0ee588a0c02f63b05b51d7d7b8cf","tid":2295422,"uid":217332,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T19:41:38.000Z","msg":"我定時會放下啲貓，佢哋又通屋跑，成日都同佢地玩捉依因。食嘢又會就住佢個份量。<br />\n唔覺得自己有虧待咗佢哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T05:05:20.000Z","msg":"明白，其實都係自己開心就好"},{"pid":"667a0e3c56b40ef13e2c8a1dec08374c66689b43","tid":2295422,"uid":193084,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"a562a5adf2c2fec86003084dc96a29a938d14ed8","tid":2295422,"uid":32577,"like":8,"dislike":3,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T01:30:11.000Z","msg":"岩呀，應該有得佢地流浪，生滿蝨，成個肚都係蟲，日灑雨淋，日日提心吊膽怕俾車撞，俾變態佬虐殺，捱餓"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T05:06:06.000Z","msg":"咁我代d小動物多謝你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b502122ab327d5599f6cbd8d79fd37985d4cfc50","tid":2295422,"uid":227788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c9e12a1f879a4b293cd60c51e0e0c8266beccfc9","tid":2295422,"uid":193084,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2fdf23be8e37ecbe0d69daab54df06988a7dfb4c","tid":2295422,"uid":227788,"like":4,"dislike":10,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T19:36:44.000Z","msg":"大部分都係為咗滿足自己嘅私慾<br />\n<br />\n全部狗公都冇曬啲睾丸 變曬公公<br />\n就係為咗唔好強姦自己隻腳<br />\n<br />\n主人虛偽咁話為咗佢好少啲病痛..."},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T05:04:31.000Z","msg":"依個問題我都諗咗好耐，我諗主要都係想佢地長命d陪你耐d<br />\n<br />\n但我喺你十幾廿歲精力旺盛果時閹咗你，話你會長命十幾廿年你肯唔肯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T05:07:20.000Z","msg":"佢哋堅持閹割貓狗 佢哋係唔會好似人類咁自卑<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n虛偽到一個點"},{"pid":"267a0927d40fb3af660d6e8ad3fb17575f83f060","tid":2295422,"uid":193084,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T05:33:31.000Z","msg":"開得喺寵物台都預咗比人負評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實我都好鍾意貓貓狗狗，但亦都見過好多劣質主人令我反思養寵物依回事<br />\n如果隻貓係比人遺棄我都支持領養，但都聽過有貓媽媽養得d仔女好地地無啦啦比人拎走咗嘅無助<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我依個post係無答案嘅，純粹想知大家嘅睇法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68454c44578fd183c0f6b988f6bc64ba41fdf9d8","tid":2295422,"uid":71253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T06:48:15.000Z","msg":"我覺得唔使將人類個套思維套落去貓個到<br />\n本身個生理構造同思維就係唔同"},{"pid":"b2c502b3ebf7b32e7c15dcb9611b2bb9e3de09ed","tid":2295422,"uid":299372,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"a562a5adf2c2fec86003084dc96a29a938d14ed8","tid":2295422,"uid":32577,"like":8,"dislike":3,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T01:30:11.000Z","msg":"岩呀，應該有得佢地流浪，生滿蝨，成個肚都係蟲，日灑雨淋，日日提心吊膽怕俾車撞，俾變態佬虐殺，捱餓"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T07:57:17.000Z","msg":"完全認同<br />\n明明周不時都有虐貓虐狗新聞<br />\n前幾日連登先有人post流浪唐狗比人斬<br />\n<br />\n點解會覺得香港流浪動物係自由自在<br />\n呢種想法我先覺得勁大愛左膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15bd1614a8468a6f778cc36fce64733cad1b0e27","tid":2295422,"uid":122915,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T08:33:28.000Z","msg":"其實本身貓狗都唔係一定由佢地自由出入<br />\n食野就識返屋企先叫正常生活<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你啲所謂正常生活係因為你見到有貓狗可以咁做<br />\n但事實唔係每隻都得<br />\n加上香港啲公園周鳩圍都有老鼠藥又有變態佬放毒藥殺動物<br />\n呢啲唔係養嘅人嘅錯 係本身成個城市有錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n對動物係咪好事係睇養嗰啲人比唔比到佢應該要有嘅生活例如散步 同隻野玩咁 照顧埋佢心理生理需要<br />\n但的確好多人係唔識做呢啲野 好多「自我」想法 「覺得」佢地係點點點<br />\n咁呢啲係一般人都有嘅問題 本身就應該要去學 但係啲人就唔學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我覺得係一半睇人一半睇動物嘅性格<br />\n如果佢天生細膽你掉佢出去自己搵食一樣好快死<br />\n你以為流浪貓狗唔會隻揪圍毆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />?"},{"pid":"683a2bf93f1393fe1b8b802bf4f8f1aef6e66b13","tid":2295422,"uid":122915,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c9e12a1f879a4b293cd60c51e0e0c8266beccfc9","tid":2295422,"uid":193084,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2fdf23be8e37ecbe0d69daab54df06988a7dfb4c","tid":2295422,"uid":227788,"like":4,"dislike":10,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T19:36:44.000Z","msg":"大部分都係為咗滿足自己嘅私慾<br